DESCRIPTION:

Near future. The political situation in the world of tense to the limit because of the extremely unpleasant incident: in the sky over Eastern Europe, the U.S. missile shot down an airliner by a commercial flight. As a result of the disaster all on board were killed. The U.S. government officially declared nothing to do with the incident. One of the most experienced agents of U.S. intelligence Michael Thorton entrusted the task to investigate and find the culprits of the tragedy to prevent a looming international conflict.
The draft Alpha Protocol player gets an opportunity not only to fully control the actions and behavior of the protagonist, but also to determine its attitude to events that influence the course of events. Implemented in the game modern combat system designed for quick decisions. These interesting features in conjunction with the possibility of intensive development of the hero and innovative role-playing elements, carefully thought-out plot, which can compete with the best works in the genre of the spy thriller, as well as detailed framework of a virtual world, which ensured the full effect of the presence, can be called the Alpha Protocol role-playing game of the new generation.
